data.title: Artist: Babyface
data.meta_description: Babyface covered Silent Night, I'll Be Home for Christmas, The Christmas Song, Sleigh Ride and other songs. Babyface originally did Silent Night, I'll Be Home for Christmas, The Christmas Song, Sleigh Ride and other songs. Babyface wrote End of the Road, When Can I See You and Love Saw It.
